{
  "stem": "717.2",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "The war is going to end as soon as the Russians come in.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They going to come and liberate us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Little did we know that they didn't give a hoot about us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But this was our dream.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "The Messiah is going to come only from there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Comrade Stalin is going to save us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "We had a party.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I remember what we got.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I, I don't know where they got this.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Everybody got a slice of bread with honey.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "That was the party to celebrate the fact that Soviet Russia went into the war against the Germans.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] The-- what was the most traumatic thing in the ghetto was the continuous, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] practically every day, different publications of instructions on what we should do, who's going to be sent away.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And every day, there were different things.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "One of the worst was a time-- and I don't remember what year.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "I think it was '42.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "It was called the [NON-ENGLISH], which is like the closing down.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "They completely shut off the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "We weren't allowed-- we didn't go to work.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "I don't remember-- it lasted quite a few days.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And the Germans just came into the homes and just ripped people out.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "First, they took the children, young children.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And the president of the ghetto, Mordechai Rumkowski, he was the king, the god of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "He came.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was a huge meeting on the-- where was it?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The plaza of the, the fire brigade, the Jewish fire brigade.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Called everybody who went there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I remember the words he said.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I still think for that alone, they should have burned him alive.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was 77 years old, and he uttered the words, Jews, a terrible tragedy befell us.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Give up your children.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
